### Create Product
POST https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Wireless Headphones",
  "description": "High quality noise-cancelling headphones",
  "price": 99.99,
  "sku": "WH-001",
  "categoryId": null
}

### Add Inventory
POST https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/inventory
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "productId": "ee04ec8d-a1a3-4941-9f78-6dd19dfdc381",
  "productName": "Wireless Headphones",
  "quantityToAdd": 100
}

### Place Order
POST https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "ee04ec8d-a1a3-4941-9f78-6dd19dfdc381",
      "productName": "Wireless Headphones",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 99.99
    }
  ]
}

### Get My Orders (lists all orders — check status field)
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Order by ID (paste real UUID from Place Order response)
GET https://event-driven-e-commerce.onrender.com/api/v1/orders/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
